                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><p class="indent"><span class="tei-persName">
                                    Theodore </span> was the bishop of <span class="tei-placeName"> Olba </span>.  <a href="/3107-17" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><p class="indent"><span class="tei-persName">
                                    Theodore </span> was bishop of <span class="tei-placeName"> Olba </span> in
